{"tid":1451013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武, 辛苦你地, 係時候接力","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:21:07.000Z","uid":305005,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c4193490a204b7e310811ed716ea797af8fdf073","tid":1451013,"uid":305005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:12:23.000Z","msg":"相信經過今晚之後, 相信本身和理非既人都想盡一分力<br />\n除左文宣外, 最好就利用今次機會, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搞多個百萬人既遊行</span></span>, 等有個平台比想幫手既和理非出黎<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: green;\">原因有四</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n1) 勇武的確會令政府暴露更多問題, 但人數太少, 需要和理非幫手 (<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非越多勇武越安全</span></span>)<br />\n<br />\n2) 部份和理非對示威者過激行為卻步 加上遊行太多唔夠集中, 令佢地難以參與 (但今晚事件已經燃點番佢地怒火, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家唔搞幾時搞</span></span>?)<br />\n<br />\n3) <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拉番埋勇武同和理非</span></span> (一支竹仔易折彎, 幾支竹仔...)<br />\n<br />\n4) 趁機製造話題 (百萬人遊行), 話比全世界, 中共, 香港政府, 更重要係班淺藍絲知, 示威唔係一小撮人, <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而係香港主流民意 </span></span>(警察今晚咁做 人人都想同佢割蓆)<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: green;\">所以</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不如我地可以叫民陣搞多次遊行?</span></span>, 因為佢地之前兩次有成功經驗 同號召力較多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">最後想講句...勇武你地從來都唔係自己一人</span></span>"},{"pid":"b7b71a6e1437f07a97a77bf654849cca1818c15b","tid":1451013,"uid":305005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:14:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1f698015dfafeed31654509d338114af61813859","tid":1451013,"uid":297097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:16:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e819e1d0e8a92844e9cc42a6060fe5595b9a72e0","tid":1451013,"uid":103476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:17:40.000Z","msg":"非常重要，借位一用<br />\n<br />\n致所有比狗打而想反抗嘅前線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1448193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1448193</a>"},{"pid":"28e66003015185903e4bbb776dacb44fbce3682b","tid":1451013,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:17:55.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9c4556860de5ae9f6988872b0c873c1d5fdb35","tid":1451013,"uid":228645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:21:07.000Z","msg":"得罪講句9/6已經大遊行過,政府嘅回應係noted with thanks啊<br />\n<br />\n和理非之前已經升級到罷工<br />\n點解突然又降返級做大遊行<br />\n<br />\n要做就諗點樣再升級"}]}